<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV70">
<l>kuntamōṭu cūlamvēlkaṟ ṟōmaraṅkaṟ ṟaṇṭuvāḷ</l>
<l>pantamāṉa tēvarkaḷpa rantuvāṉa kammuṟa</l>
<l>vantavāṇa ṉīraiñnūṟu tōḷkaḷaittu ṇittanā</l>
<l>ḷantavanta vākulama mararēya ṟivarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The day [He] severed the thousand arms of Bāṇa who came [attacking],</l>
<l>In such a way that the gods connected [to him] spread out</l>
<l rend="indent">And reached the celestial world</l>
<l>[with their] pikes, tridents, spears, large clubs, pestles, [and] swords,</l>
<l>Only the immortals would know of their respective sorrow!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
